-- Spanish Regions Ask for Better ICO Credit Terms, Expansion Says
-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 2012-02-20T07:19:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/spanish-regions-ask-for-better-ico-credit-terms-expansion-says.html
Spanish regional governments have
asked the central government to improve the terms of a credit
line from the state-run Official Credit Institute, Expansion
reported. *Regional governments say interest rate too high,
*Want repayment schedule extended, Expansion said without saying
how it got the information  To contact the reporter on this story:
